":"1233","1277":"1277","1221":"1221","1243":"1243","1229":"1229","1218":"1218","Offaly, Ireland":"County Offaly, Irlande","Ireland":"Irlande","Athy, County Kildare, Ireland":"Athy, County Kildare, Irlande","Aberdare, Mid Glamorgan, Wales":"Aberdare, Mid Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Youghal, Cork, Ireland":"Youghal, County Cork, Irlande","County Mayo, Ireland":"County Mayo, Irlande","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Thomas Fitz Maurice est né en 1216, à Irlande, son père, Maurice FitzGerald de Berminham 2nd Lord of Offaly, avait 22 ans et sa mère, Juliana Cogan, avait 17 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Rohese St Michael. Il est décédé en 1271, à County Mayo, Irlande, à l’âge de 55 ans."},"de":{"1216–1271":"1216–1271","1215–1243":"1215–1243","1218–1277":"1218–1277","1221–Male":"1221–Verstorben","1229–1271":"1229–1271","1233–1316":"1233–1316","1250–1316":"1250–1316","1269–Female":"1269–Verstorben","1194–1257":"1194–1257","1200–1257":"1200–1257","20 May 1257":"20. Mai 1257","1250":"1250","1271":"1271","1194":"1194","1316":"1316","1216":"1216","1215":"1215","1269":"1269","1214":"1214","1257":"1257","1200":"1200","1233":"1233","1277":"1277","1221":"1221","1243":"1243","1229":"1229","1218":"1218","Offaly, Ireland":"County Offaly, Irland","Ireland":"Irland","Athy, County Kildare, Ireland":"Athy, County Kildare, Irland","Aberdare, Mid Glamorgan, Wales":"Aberdare, Mid Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom","Youghal, Cork, Ireland":"Youghal, County Cork, Irland","County Mayo, Ireland":"County Mayo, Irland","lifeSummary":"Als Thomas Fitz Maurice 1216 in Irland geboren wurde, war sein Vater Maurice FitzGerald de Berminham 2nd Lord of Offaly 22 und seine Mutter Juliana Cogan 17. Er hatte mit Rohese St Michael mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter. Er starb 1271 im Alter von 55 Jahren in County Mayo, Irland."},"ht":{"1216–1271":"1216–1271","1215–1243":"1215–1243","1218–1277":"1218–1277","1221–Male":"1221–Desede","1229–1271":"1229–1271","1233–1316":"1233–1316","1250–1316":"1250–